title: Dream Jobs and Dish With Denny Directo
description:
This week, Lauren welcomes fellow Entertainment Tonight on-air talent Denny Directo to the podcast! Denny and Lauren dive into what he did to get his dream job at ET, and evaluate whether our traditional paths to success hold up today. And as two entertainment news reporters, they have to dish on and dissect the latest celebrity news, including Pete Davidson potentially being Kim Kardashian's Kanye rebound, Britney Spears' bombshell blaming the conservatorship on her mother and more.
